[prefer-takeuntil]: subscribe within a component must be preceded by takeUntil
[prefer-takeuntil-no-subject]: takeUntil argument must be a property of the class, e.g. takeUntil(this.destroy$)
[prefer-takeuntil-no-destroy]: component containing subscribe must implement the ngOnDestroy() method
[prefer-takeuntil-no-next]: there must be an invocation of this._destroy$.next() in ngOnDestroy()
[prefer-takeuntil-no-complete]: there must be an invocation of this._destroy$.complete() in ngOnDestroy()
